caa/littlesun.webp 640w,\n/Balalachen.github.io/static/e2efe915414d9a7ebc49f0b39a396572/12585/littlesun.webp 1280w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"(min-width: 640px) 640px, 100vw"}]},"width":640,"height":480}}},"icon":["youtube","website"],"url":["https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=CRdhppLBLKw","https://www.ncl.edu.tw/information_237_10863.html"],"awards":["[a] 2020 XR創新金典大賞 最佳XR文化藝術應用","2020 Laval Virtual Revolution Student Competition"],"exhibitions":["2020 台北資訊月主題館","2019 閱讀嘉年華","2019 科普論壇 -「邁向智慧世代-科技Fun新玩」","2019 新竹實驗中學 教學展示"]},{"name":"神遊敦煌-莫高窟第61窟","description":"敦煌石窟是一座已有1600年歷史的藝術寶庫。為了保護且延長敦煌石窟的壽命，現今石窟的開放時間是有限制的，有些重點石窟甚至不會開放給一般民眾參觀。為了讓更多人能夠有機會欣賞敦煌石窟之美，臺大與中研院的研究團隊結合敦煌研究院的研究人員，共同展開VR內容研製計畫。此VR作品除了讓大家能以虛擬逼真的方式探索莫高窟第61窟，也透過數位復原技術去重建那些受損的壁畫與塑像，讓大家得以使用「復原探照燈」去觀賞那些重建後栩栩如生的壁畫與塑像。例如，莫高窟第61窟之中，中央壇上目前已毀損不復存在的文殊菩薩塑像群，即可透過數位復原技術重現於虛擬石窟中。此外，在探索虛擬石窟時，亦可啟動西壁的〈五台山圖〉壁畫與北壁的〈華嚴經變〉壁畫之動畫解說，以深入瞭解壁畫背後的故事。","selection":false,"status":"live","position":"Technical Consultant","tags":["Unity SRP","CSharp","HLSL"],"image":null,"icon":["steam","youtube","website"],"url":["https://store.steampowered.com/app/947240/61/?l=tchinese","https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xTZzsbO447I","http://www.ntuimlab.tw/dunhuang/"],"awards":null,"exhibitions":null}]},"publications":{"nodes":[{"title":"Haptic around: multiple tactile sensations for immersive environment and interaction in virtual reality","authors":"Ping-Hsuan Han, Yang-Sheng Chen, Kong-Chang Lee, Hao-Cheng Wang, Chiao-En Hsieh, Jui-Chun Hsiao, Chien-Hsing Chou, Yi-Ping Hung","proceedings":"VRST 18'","published":"28 November 2018","selection":true,"award":null,"dwlink":null,"videolink":null},{"title":"Soes: Attachable augmented haptic on gaming controller for immersive interaction","authors":"Yang-Sheng Chen, Ping-Hsuan Han, Jui-Chun Hsiao, Kong-Chang Lee, Chiao-En Hsieh, Kuan-Yin Lu, Chien-Hsing Chou, Yi-Ping Hung","proceedings":"UIST 16'","published":"16 October 2016","selection":true,"award":"Best Demo Award","dwlink":"https://dl.acm.org/doi/10.1